<li id="cite_note-72"><b><a href="#cite_ref-72" title="">^</a></b> Red Hat discusses RHEL's inclusion of SELinux: <a href="http://www.redhat.com/magazine/006apr05/features/selinux/" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.redhat.com/magazine/006apr05/features/selinux/" rel="nofollow">[1]</a> A wiki devoted to SELinux in Fedora:<a href="http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/SELinux" class="external autonumber" title="http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/SELinux" rel="nofollow">[2]</a> A review of CentOS hosted at linux.com: <a href="http://distrocenter.linux.com/article.pl?sid=05/05/03/1548207&amp;tid=127" class="external autonumber" title="http://distrocenter.linux.com/article.pl?sid=05/05/03/1548207&amp;tid=127" rel="nofollow">[3]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-73"><b><a href="#cite_ref-73" title="">^</a></b> For instance see this paragraph in <a href="/wiki/Debian" title="Debian">Debian</a> Policy <a href="http://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-files.html#s10.9" class="external autonumber" title="http://www.debian.org/doc/debian-policy/ch-files.html#s10.9" rel="nofollow">[4]</a> (a better citation is welcome)</li>
<li id="cite_note-74"><b><a href="#cite_ref-74" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb457115.aspx" class="external text" title="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb457115.aspx" rel="nofollow">"Managing Authorization and Access Control"</a>. Microsoft Technet<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb457115.aspx" class="external free" title="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb457115.aspx" rel="nofollow">http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb457115.aspx</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Managing+Authorization+and+Access+Control&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Microsoft+Technet&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ftechnet.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Flibrary%2Fbb457115.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Comparison_of_Windows_and_Linux"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-75"><b><a href="#cite_ref-75" title="">^</a></b> Microsoft describes in detail the steps taken to combat this in a TechNet bulletin. <a href="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/windowsvista/aa905073.aspx" class="external autonumber" title="http://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/windowsvista/aa905073.aspx" rel="nofollow">[5]</a></li>
<li id="cite_note-kennykerr-76"><b><a href="#cite_ref-kennykerr_76-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFKenny_Kerr2006">Kenny Kerr (2006-09-29). <a href="http://weblogs.asp.net/kennykerr/archive/2006/09/29/Windows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx" class="external text" title="http://weblogs.asp.net/kennykerr/archive/2006/09/29/Windows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx" rel="nofollow">"Windows Vista for Developers – Part 4 – User Account Control"</a><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://weblogs.asp.net/kennykerr/archive/2006/09/29/Windows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx" class="external free" title="http://weblogs.asp.net/kennykerr/archive/2006/09/29/Windows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx" rel="nofollow">http://weblogs.asp.net/kennykerr/archive/2006/09/29/Windows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-03-15</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Windows+Vista+for+Developers+%E2%80%93+Part+4+%E2%80%93+User+Account+Control&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Kenny+Kerr&amp;rft.au=Kenny+Kerr&amp;rft.date=2006-09-29&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fweblogs.asp.net%2Fkennykerr%2Farchive%2F2006%2F09%2F29%2FWindows-Vista-for-Developers-_1320_-Part-4-_1320_-User-Account-Control.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Comparison_of_Windows_and_Linux"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
